text: KYTE or Kyte could refer to: *KYTE, a radio station (102.7 FM) licensed to Independence, Oregon, United States *Kyte, a rock group from Leicestershire, England *Kyte (surname) *KUFO (AM), a radio station (970 AM) licensed to Portland, Oregon, United States, known as KYTE from 1977 to 1990 *KXL-FM, a radio station (101.1 FM) licensed to Portland, Oregon, United States, known as KYTE-FM from 1977 to 1979 and from 1985 to 1989 *Kyte Group, a financial services company *Kyte, Norway, a village in the municipality of Voss in Hordaland county, Norway *Kyte River, tributary of the Rock River
title: KYTE (disambiguation)
